{"tid":1802942,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"楊潤雄:校長態度和立場 如果我們認為校長已經不能勝任，可以取消他的校長資格","createTime":"2019-12-29T23:12:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T01:38:12.000Z","uid":249945,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"04db5af87dacf61935321206ba448b343192000e","tid":1802942,"uid":249945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T23:12:42.000Z","msg":"【全文閱讀】<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2F2aLwD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2F2aLwD&d=OJrKX0dn%2BAqYJaSYBqJK9xdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=0f3f9721\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2F2aLwD</a>  //  教育局局長楊潤雄接受內地媒體《上觀新聞》訪問（屬上海《解放日報》旗下），被問到「如果要求學校對教師進行調查，學校卻不配合，甚至校長自己也支持教師的行為，教育局如何應對？」楊潤雄說：「學校的基本態度如何、是否支持教師，其實很容易看出来。比如學校在反饋中認為涉事教師『沒有問題』，我們就可以知道，學校、校長態度和立場可能『有問題』，然後從管理角度去處理。」<br />\n<br />\n「如果我們認為校長已經不能勝任，可以取消他的校長資格。每個校長都是由教育局常任秘書長委任的，所以我們在法律上有這樣的權力，但行使時會十分謹慎。如果他情節嚴重，連當一個教師也不合適了，我們還可以取消他的教師資格。如果程度並不嚴重，我們會反饋給學校的辦學團體，建議辦學團體、校董共同幫助校長做好工作。」楊潤雄又說：「此外我們還有一項權力，就是可以直接委任校董加入一所學校的校董委員會，參與學校日常管理。」<br />\n<br />\n【全文閱讀】<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2F2aLwD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2F2aLwD&d=OJrKX0dn%2BAqYJaSYBqJK9xdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=0f3f9721\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2F2aLwD</a><br />\n－－－－－－－－<br />\n新聞戰線艱巨漫長，我們需要各位的支持，請立即訂閱，成為眾新聞長期訂戶。<br />\n訂戶服務詳情：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/訂閲我們\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F%E8%A8%82%E9%96%B2%E6%88%91%E5%80%91&d=OJrKX0dn%2BAqYJaSYBqJK9xdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=7add084c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/訂閲我們</a>"},{"pid":"88e351b8c5a93fa33515c1da2901bc26a4182b3e","tid":1802942,"uid":249945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T23:15:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c09d570ebf2e92ec7ba5b8a2736139be13389eb","tid":1802942,"uid":249945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T23:18:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f39a9c0093a8b964be59388d1c9c11ffc8817dbf","tid":1802942,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T23:32:24.000Z","msg":"哩啲咪國際線囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"497030b1c5f160afde239669099a92c05072a84c","tid":1802942,"uid":249945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T01:38:12.000Z","msg":"push"}]}